      <title>中国工厂活动再次萎缩 给经济带来警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/china-factory-activity-shrinks-again-in-warning-to-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[6 月份，中国制造业活动连续第二个月萎缩，表明中国政府寄希望于推动经济发展的这一领域出现疲软迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/china-factory-activity-shrinks-again-in-warning-to-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 01:51:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡最后一个 18 洞公共高尔夫球场因重建而关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/singapore-has-only-one-public-golf-course-left-as-marina-bay-site-closes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡本周末关闭了其最后一座公共 18 洞高尔夫球场，由于政府的土地再开发计划，滨海湾球场俯瞰着这个金融中心的天际线，因此被关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/singapore-has-only-one-public-golf-course-left-as-marina-bay-site-closes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业率随工资增长而放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/world-economy-latest-us-employment-seen-moderating-along-with-wage-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[6 月份，美国雇主可能在工资增长放缓的同时减少了招聘，这对杰罗姆·鲍威尔及其美联储同事来说是一个有利的发展，他们正在寻求更多证据证明通胀正在放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/world-economy-latest-us-employment-seen-moderating-along-with-wage-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
